{"tid":1201592,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我想問 搞立法會真係有用咩","createTime":"2019-06-11T05:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T02:22:08.000Z","uid":37679,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"4a25c89b92deb081a65197a259e0415dce37310d","tid":1201592,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:30:29.000Z","msg":"你包圍立法會 阻唔到入面開會 冇用<br />\n就算攻到入去佢地行後門轉場會議<br />\n條修例一樣係過<br />\n就算聽日三讀唔到 第日都會三讀到<br />\n喺一個咁易俾龜包圍清場既位做得啲乜野<br />\n我唔係反對去發起任何行動<br />\n係呢個行動既成效有幾大<br />\n<br />\n橫掂都要搞 橫掂都要俾人清<br />\n點解唔揀個玩得耐啲既方法<br />\n<br />\n就係堵塞主要幹道<br />\n<br />\n一係要避免佢地轉場開會但我地仲on99咁留喺立法會<br />\n二係順手幫人罷工罷市<br />\n三上次其實啲龜係冇我地乎 我地要撤純粹因爲禁制令<br />\n<br />\n上次分開兩個地點 分薄左人手同物資<br />\n所以如果今次係搞 就應該集中一個地方<br />\n俾人清 就全體一齊轉場繼續<br />\n就算知道好大機會輸 都要煩到佢地仆街"},{"pid":"95dbde33251c500a70034d2e29eaf3170ae0f807","tid":1201592,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:34:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aee57d4622db338205461cd2a24efa611b1e5a3d","tid":1201592,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:35:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9466fb777edd32a1193da40fb2eadd018ed5a752","tid":1201592,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:39:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46e1fcb3a8fdb5ebfa435cc4bdd1d61fe712815d","tid":1201592,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:39:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"983c451a7a80ef64e8046246af257c0297ba77e6","tid":1201592,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"73451a5eb211957bbf5e156573101ba99701203c","tid":1201592,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T05:42:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56573aa0fbf43d8d0b8c0306fd97076d64c9c728","tid":1201592,"uid":37679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T06:10:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c9285c66b122433cd69ffc2d73